  <text>
    <body>
      <div type="page" n="163">
        <pb n="163"/>
        <lg xml:id="block_A" xml:lang="en" facs="https://momoiro.hallyu.io/mishkan/iiif/3/mishkan%2F26115641-5696-4140-a029-ab0b4657cfe8.jp2/1336,1227,2813,767/max/0/default.jpg">
          <l>WE ARE A PEOPLE in whom the past endures,</l>
          <l>in whom the present is inconceivable without moments gone by.</l>
          <l>The Exodus lasted a moment, a moment enduring forever.</l>
          <l>What happened once upon a time happens all the time.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg xml:id="block_B" xml:lang="en" facs="https://momoiro.hallyu.io/mishkan/iiif/3/mishkan%2F26115641-5696-4140-a029-ab0b4657cfe8.jp2/1357,2432,2233,824/max/0/default.jpg">
          <l>A THOUGHT has blown the market place away.</l>
          <l>There is a song on the wind and joy in the trees.</l>
          <l>Shabbat arrives in the world,</l>
          <l>scattering a song in the silence of the night:</l>
          <l>Eternity utters a day.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg xml:id="block_C" xml:lang="en" facs="https://momoiro.hallyu.io/mishkan/iiif/3/mishkan%2F26115641-5696-4140-a029-ab0b4657cfe8.jp2/929,6008,3611,250/max/0/default.jpg">
          <l>More than the Jewish People has kept Shabbat, Shabbat has kept the Jewish People. Ahad Ha-Am</l>
        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
  </text>
</TEI>